          "description": "PEPE is a community-driven meme token inspired by the internet character Pepe the Frog, a well-known figure in online meme culture. Launched in April 2023, the project aims to embrace the lighthearted and humorous side of cryptocurrency by creating a token centered around internet culture and community engagement. Rather than focusing on complex use cases or utility, PEPE is built around the idea of shared fun and cultural relevance."
